Class TestSystem

java.lang.Object
test.TestSystem
public class TestSystem extends Object
Test class for the MyFoodora system. This class contains tests to ensure the correct initialization and functionality of the MyFoodora system. It uses JUnit for testing.
Author:
Aymane Adib
